sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant GA as GitHub Actions
    participant DH as Docker Hub
    participant Git as Git Repository
    participant Argo as Argo CD
    participant K8s as Kubernetes

    Dev->>GH: Push to feature branch
    GH->>GA: Trigger PR Validation
    GA-->>GH: ✓ Validation passed
    Dev->>GH: Merge to main
    GH->>GA: Trigger App CI/CD
    GA->>GA: Policy validation (OPA + Kyverno)
    GA->>GA: Docker build (multi-arch)
    GA->>GA: Trivy scan + SBOM generation
    GA->>DH: Push images (v1.x.x)
    GA->>Git: Update values.yaml (new tag)
    Git-->>Argo: Detect config drift
    Argo->>K8s: Sync new image tags
    K8s->>K8s: Rolling update pods
    K8s-->>Argo: ✓ Healthy